*Co-Owner *Median Coder *Newb Coder *Java Programer *MySQL Programer

What Is RuneWorld?

What Positions Can I Apply For?

*Co-Owner
*Median Coder
*Newb Coder
*Java Programer
*MySQL Programer

Why are you doing this?
To be honest, I just think it will be fun. Im NOT doing this to raise money, although donations are accepted, BUT NOT NEEDED!

How many people will join?
As many people that we, as a TEAM promote, will possiably join the server.

I Like It. Am I Promised a Job?
